data.description: **MULTIPLE OFFERS, HIGHEST AND BEST DUE BY 5PM SUN, 12/31** Investor special! Tucked into a quiet suburb in Cape Coral, this four bedroom, two bathroom home has over 2300 square feet under air, with a split floorplan, an open-concept kitchen/dining/living room area, a formal dining room that would make a fabulous office, and even a pool in the back. Deferred maintenance makes this an as-is sale, perfect for an investor. Don't wait - snag this steal of a deal before it's gone!
